Recon -ng is a favourite and most used tool used by the Hackers & Attackers

-> Recon -ng is a inbuilt linux tool that is used to find the details of the subdomains of the target website 

-> Recon -ng is a full-featured reconnaissance framework designed to provide a powerful environment to conduct web-based reconnaissance quickly and thoroughly.

-> It assists attackers in gathering information from public source-code repositories.

-> using this tools user can find the locations as well the ip address of the target website 

